HARD TO FIND 2 BRS WITH 1 1/2 BATHS PLUS OUTDOOR KITCHEN. Fifth Wheel - 3 SLIDEOUTS. Sleeps 8. Rockwood 8301WS More pictures available.

1 ½ Bathrooms. Amazing Outdoor kitchen. 2 Entrances. Triple Slideouts. Bunk Room. High Ceilings. Large awning. Outdoor shower. Pass through basement storage. Fireplace. 2 TVs, with room for another in the main bedroom and one outside. Exterior speakers. Extra Large Dinette. Sleeps 8. 

OUTDOOR KITCHEN includes refrigerator, sink, 2 burner gas range plus storage.  Great place to plug in your coffee maker and toaster. The pull up door provides cover for sun and/or rain. We set up a Blackstone right next to the outdoor kitchen it and do most of the cooking outside.

THE HALF BATH has a door to the interior bunk room and to the exterior which is great for the tent lover family to use in lieu of entry through the main door.

BUNK ROOM - Private Single over single bed. TV. Access to half bath.

KITCHEN AND COOKING The dinette is extra large and can seat 6 easily. (more little ones) 8 foot table fits between exterior door and outdoor kitchen for camp staging area.

MAIN BEDROOM with Queen bed, mirrored closet plus extra storage cabinetry.  Sliding door to main bathroom. Storage under bed. Tall ceiling in main bedroom.
 
VERY CLEAN AND TASTEFUL INTERIOR. 

2017 Forest River RV Rockwood Signature ULTRA LITE 8301WS, Forest River Rockwood Signature Ultra Lite fifth wheel 8301WS highlights:- Triple Slide Outs- Rear Bunk Room- Bath and a Half- Two Entry Doors- Outdoor Kitchen. The outside kitchen features a refrigerator, sink, and a two-burner swing-out stove. Your kids will love having their own space in the rear bunk house! Here there is a slide out with a top bunk and a flip-down bunk. You will also find a convenient half bathroom located off the bunk house. There is also a private outside entry door. The full size bathroom is located at the top of the stairs. It includes a sink with a medicine cabinet, radius shower, toilet, and a sliding door which leads into the main bedroom. Enjoy the convenience of a power awning complemented by LED lights. Seamless one-piece roof that adds durability and style. Basement storage. Reese revolution hitch.

Included link to video is not our unit but is a great representation of the floorplan. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yrWm8sxxahk
